Skill content
-------------
The four upstream-referenced skills (deep-research, academic-paper,
academic-paper-reviewer, academic-pipeline) are not vendored or forked. The
SKILL.md files in this package under skills/<slug>/ are thin manifests that
point to the upstream paths at the pinned commit and carry a sha256
contentHash for drift detection. The runtime fetches the upstream content on
demand at invocation. See `make bump SHA=<new-sha>` for the upgrade path.

The four port-original skills (intake-triage, pipeline-orchestration,
checkpoint-coordination, escalation-routing) are hand-authored in this
repository and have no upstream counterpart. They are owned by the CEO role
and were authored as part of this port.

